<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <%- include('partials/head') %>
</head>
<body>
  <%- include('partials/header') %>

  <main>
    <section class="page-header">
      <div class="container">
        <h1 class="page-header__title">Why Choose Us</h1>
        <p class="page-header__breadcrumb"><a href="/">Home</a> / Why Us</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section" aria-label="Our Features">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="text-center">
          <span class="section__label">Our Advantages</span>
          <h2 class="section__title">What Makes Us Special</h2>
          <p class="section__subtitle">Discover the unique benefits that set Taleem Ul Quran apart from other online academies.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="features-grid">
          <div class="feature-card fade-in">
            <div class="feature-card__icon">
              <img src="/images/Feature_pic/desired_timing_logo.png" alt="" aria-hidden="true" width="40" height="40">
            </div>
            <h3 class="feature-card__title">Flexible Timing</h3>
            <p class="feature-card__text">Customize your Quran learning schedule to fit your lifestyle. Feeling tired after work or busy in the morning? Simply let us know your preferred timings, and we'll tailor our classes to suit your needs.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="feature-card fade-in">
            <div class="feature-card__icon">
              <img src="/images/pics/girl.png" alt="" aria-hidden="true" width="40" height="40">
            </div>
            <h3 class="feature-card__title">Female Teachers</h3>
            <p class="feature-card__text">Highly qualified female Quran tutors are available to teach children and female students, offering expertise in Quranic studies and fostering a supportive learning environment for spiritual growth.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="feature-card fade-in">
            <div class="feature-card__icon">
              <img src="/images/Feature_pic/any_device_logo.png" alt="" aria-hidden="true" width="40" height="40">
            </div>
            <h3 class="feature-card__title">Any Device, Anywhere</h3>
            <p class="feature-card__text">We use the latest software like MS Teams and Zoom. Classes work on any electronic device — computer, smartphone, or tablet. With screen sharing, take your classes anywhere you like!</p>
          </div>

          <div class="feature-card fade-in">
            <div class="feature-card__icon">
              <img src="/images/Feature_pic/indivisual_session_logo.png" alt="" aria-hidden="true" width="40" height="40">
            </div>
            <h3 class="feature-card__title">Individual Sessions</h3>
            <p class="feature-card__text">Every student receives special attention with one-on-one sessions. We don't prefer large congregations for online learning. However, sessions for siblings or family members are also available.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="feature-card fade-in">
            <div class="feature-card__icon">
              <img src="/images/Feature_pic/staff_logo.png" alt="" aria-hidden="true" width="40" height="40">
            </div>
            <h3 class="feature-card__title">Qualified Staff</h3>
            <p class="feature-card__text">Our engaging curriculum, crafted by qualified staff, provides dynamic learning experiences. Our tutors inspire a love for Quranic studies, fostering understanding and connection to the sacred text.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="feature-card fade-in">
            <div class="feature-card__icon">
              <img src="/images/Feature_pic/affordable_fee_logo .png" alt="" aria-hidden="true" width="40" height="40">
            </div>
            <h3 class="feature-card__title">Affordable Fees</h3>
            <p class="feature-card__text">Our affordable plans, complemented by family discounts for siblings, prioritize accessibility to quality Quranic education. Flexible payment options and transparent pricing ensure learning remains achievable.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section section--alt" aria-label="Start Now">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="cta-banner fade-in">
          <h2 class="cta-banner__title">Experience the Difference</h2>
          <p class="cta-banner__text">Start with a free 3-day trial and see why families worldwide trust Taleem Ul Quran for their children's Quranic education.</p>
          <a href="/register" class="btn btn--accent btn--lg">Start Free Trial</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>
